Works standalone and via mai changelog dispatch\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] go build ./cmd/mai-changelog/\n- [ ] Create 3 entries, mai-changelog merge produces valid markdown\n- [ ] Migrate .tinychange/ from trek, verify entry count matches\n- [ ] mai changelog new works via dispatch","timestamp":"2026-04-04T13:13:36Z","branch":"main"}

